Här kommer Guiden till hur man bränner PS2 och DVDR filer i ISO el IMG format
Jag använder Nero 6 vilket jag tycker är lättast :P

1. Öppna Nero 6 Burning Rom
2. Det kommer upp ett fönster stäng ner det.
3. Sen tar du Recorder > Burn Image > Iso file.
4. Bränn sedan på en låghastighet för bästa resultat.....

For å spille dette spillet på en emulator(en decoder til pcen/datoren, som gjør at du kan spille ps2 spill på pcn) må du brenne isoen ut og putte in skivan på ny starte emulatoren
(Den beste heter PCsx2 0.7 og fungerer fint til dette spillet, du finner den her på trackern.) så må du åpne  en .Elf fil på cd-skivan! Bang så spiller du san andreas på pc... 6 mnd før det kommer ut!!!! Hehe :):):):):):):):)

)The .elf file are the executables of the demos/games.( like the .exe files in Win32 OS ) 

2) To extract an ISO from the disk , use Isobuster ( http://www.smart-projects.net/isobuster/ ) which supports both creating iso files from cd's and dvd's. It's a freeware version. 

3) In commercials games, the executable doesnt have the .elf extension. 
To find it, open the file SYSTEM.CNF in the ISO/BIN or in the Cd/DVD itself ( with Notepad for exemple ) 
Look at the line : 
BOOT2 = cdrom0:SLPS_000.00;1 
( Note: , this line is just an exemple) 
SLPS_000.00 is the .elf file you are looking for. 
Extract it from the ISO or copy it from the Cd/DVD and rename it "Something.elf". 


4) nSX2 0.07.0 can't load and run ISO files. 
You must do it manually. 
Click "Load ISO" , and select the ISO. 
Click "Load Elf" , and select the previously extracted Elf. 


5)COMMERCIALS GAMES DON'T RUN. 
( maybe if you are lucky , you can see some Loading Screens, like the MK5 one
